      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** * The double negation modality *)\n\n(** The operation sending [X] to [~~X] is a modality.  This is Exercise 7.12 in the book.  Note that it is (apparently) *not* accessible unless we assume propositional resizing. *)\n"
