    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** By definition, the local types for this modality are the types such that [not_not_unit : P -> ~~P] is an equivalence.  These are exactly the stable propositions, i.e. those propositions [P] such that [~~P -> P]. *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition inO_notnot `{Funext} (P : Type)\n  : In NotNot P <~> (Stable P * IsHProp P)\n  := equiv_isequiv_not_not_unit_stable_hprop P.",
      "messages": [],
